articles.title: Shubman Gill's Reaction After KL Rahul Hits Ball Out Of Stadium During 2nd ODI Against AUS Goes Viral – WATCH - Times Now
articles.description: KL Rahul was on fire in the second India-Australia ODI, which was played at the Holkar Stadium in Indore on Sunday (September 24). During his stay at the crease, he faced a total of 38 balls to score 52 runs and hammered as many as three fours and three sixes.

articles.title: 'SKY is my dad': Cameron Green's old video goes viral after Suryakumar Yadav's destructive knock against Australia | Mint - Mint
articles.description: Popularly known as SKY, Suryakumar Yadav was at his best hitting six 6s and six 4s, while score a thunderous 72 in just 37 balls at a strike rate of 194.59, that led India to score 399/5 runs.
